                    <li><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>250 AI messages / month</li>
                    <li><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>AI session generation</li>
                    <li><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Training plans (up to 12 weeks)</li>
                    <li><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Create groups &amp; challenges</li>
                    <li><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Advanced analytics</li>
                    <li><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Overtraining analysis</li>
                    <li><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Priority support</li>
                </ul>
                <a href="/en/login/" class="btn-pricing primary">Subscribe to Pro</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Comparison Table -->
    <section class="comparison-section">
        <h2>Detailed Comparison</h2>
        <div class="comparison-table-wrapper">
        <table class="comparison-table">
            <thead><tr><th>Feature</th><th>Free</th><th>Pro</th></tr></thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr><td>Session recording</td><td class="check">&#10003;</td><td class="check">&#10003;</td></tr>
                <tr><td>Basic progress tracking</td><td class="check">&#10003;</td><td class="check">&#10003;</td></tr>
                <tr><td>Community access</td><td class="check">&#10003;</td><td class="check">&#10003;</td></tr>
                <tr><td>AI messages</td><td>3 / month</td><td>250 / month</td></tr>
                <tr><td>AI session generation</td><td class="cross">&mdash;</td><td class="check">&#10003;</td></tr>
                <tr><td>Training plans</td><td class="cross">&mdash;</td><td>Up to 12 weeks</td></tr>
                <tr><td>Create groups &amp; challenges</td><td class="cross">&mdash;</td><td class="check">&#10003;</td></tr>
                <tr><td>Advanced analytics</td><td class="cross">&mdash;</td><td class="check">&#10003;</td></tr>
                <tr><td>Overtraining analysis</td><td class="cross">&mdash;</td><td class="check">&#10003;</td></tr>
                <tr><td>Overtraining analysis</td><td class="cross">&mdash;</td><td class="check">&#10003;</td></tr>
                <tr><td>Priority support</td><td class="cross">&mdash;</td><td class="check">&#10003;</td></tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Download QR Code -->
    <section class="qr-section" style="padding: 4rem 2rem; text-align: center;">
        <h2 style="font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--gray-900); margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Download on your mobile</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--gray-500); font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; max-width: 450px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">Scan the QR code with your phone's camera to install AIVancePro.</p>
        <div style="display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 2rem; flex-wrap: wrap;">
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <canvas id="qrAppStore" width="160" height="160" style="border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--border); background: white; padding: 8px;"></canvas>
                <p style="margin-top: 0.75rem; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--gray-700);">App Store</p>
            </div>
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <canvas id="qrPlayStore" width="160" height="160" style="border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--border); background: white; padding: 8px;"></canvas>
                <p style="margin-top: 0.75rem; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--gray-700);">Google Play</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <script is:inline>
    (function(){
      function drawQR(canvasId, text) {
        var c = document.getElementById(canvasId);
        if (!c) return;
        var ctx = c.getContext('2d');
        var s = c.width;
        ctx.fillStyle = '#ffffff';
        ctx.fillRect(0, 0, s, s);
        ctx.fillStyle = '#4A90D9';
        ctx.font = 'bold 14px Inter, sans-serif';
        ctx.textAlign = 'center';
        ctx.fillText('Scan with', s/2, s/2 - 20);
        ctx.fillText('your device', s/2, s/2);
        ctx.font = '11px Inter, sans-serif';
        ctx.fillStyle = '#6a6a80';
        var short = text.length > 30 ? text.substring(0, 30) + '...' : text;
        ctx.fillText(short, s/2, s/2 + 30);
      }
      var script = document.createElement('script');
      script.src = 'https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/qrcode-generator@1.4.4/qrcode.min.js';
      script.onload = function() {
        function renderQR(canvasId, text) {
          var c = document.getElementById(canvasId);
          if (!c || typeof qrcode === 'undefined') return;
          var qr = qrcode(0, 'M');
          qr.addData(text);
          qr.make();
          var ctx = c.getContext('2d');
          var size = c.width;
          var pad = 12;
          var modules = qr.getModuleCount();
          var cellSize = (size - pad * 2) / modules;
          ctx.fillStyle = '#ffffff';
          ctx.fillRect(0, 0, size, size);
          for (var r = 0; r < modules; r++) {
            for (var col = 0; col < modules; col++) {
              if (qr.isDark(r, col)) {
                ctx.fillStyle = '#1a1a2e';
                ctx.fillRect(pad + col * cellSize, pad + r * cellSize, cellSize, cellSize);
              }
            }
          }
        }
        renderQR('qrAppStore', 'https://apps.apple.com/app/aivancepro/id6756116760');
        renderQR('qrPlayStore', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.aivancepro.app');
      };
      script.onerror = function() {
        drawQR('qrAppStore', 'apps.apple.com/aivancepro');
        drawQR('qrPlayStore', 'play.google.com/aivancepro');
      };
      document.head.appendChild(script);
    })();
    </script>

    <!-- FAQ Pricing -->
    <section class="faq-section">
        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions About Pricing</h2>
        <div class="faq-list">
            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
                    Can I change plans at any time?
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.23 7.21a.75.75 0 011.06.02L10 11.168l3.71-3.938a.75.75 0 111.08 1.04l-4.25 4.5a.75.75 0 01-1.08 0l-4.25-4.5a.75.75 0 01.02-1.06z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
                </button>
                <div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">Yes, you can upgrade to Pro or switch back to Free at any time. The change takes effect immediately.</div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
                    Is there a commitment?
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.23 7.21a.75.75 0 011.06.02L10 11.168l3.71-3.938a.75.75 0 111.08 1.04l-4.25 4.5a.75.75 0 01-1.08 0l-4.25-4.5a.75.75 0 01.02-1.06z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
                </button>
                <div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">No commitment. You can cancel your subscription at any time from the App Store or Google Play.</div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
                    Is the Free plan really free?
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.23 7.21a.75.75 0 011.06.02L10 11.168l3.71-3.938a.75.75 0 111.08 1.04l-4.25 4.5a.75.75 0 01-1.08 0l-4.25-4.5a.75.75 0 01.02-1.06z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
                </button>
                <div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">Absolutely. The Free plan gives you access to session tracking, 240+ exercises and basic statistics, with no time limit and no credit card required.</div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
                    How does payment work?
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.23 7.21a.75.75 0 011.06.02L10 11.168l3.71-3.938a.75.75 0 111.08 1.04l-4.25 4.5a.75.75 0 01-1.08 0l-4.25-4.5a.75.75 0 01.02-1.06z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
                </button>
                <div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">Payment is handled directly by the App Store (iOS) or Google Play (Android). Your subscription renews automatically each month unless cancelled.</div></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</BaseLayout>